488
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,330
Dia mudah dikenali.

489
00:26:13,350 --> 00:26:14,560
Hutan itu begitu besar.

490
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:16,470
Bagaimana cara kami
menemukannya?

491
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:19,110
